public static enum StatementBlockScope.Owner

Defines constants for all possible owners of a statement block scope.

Dieter Habelitz

COMPOUND_STATEMENT

public static final StatementBlockScope.Owner COMPOUND_STATEMENT
Constant for a statement block scope that belongs to a compound statement.

A compound statement may be a nested statement block or a statement block following an if statement, a while statement and so on.

Note that there are explicitly defined constants for try statement, catch clause and finally clause statement block scopes.
